    "audio_narration": "string"
  },
  "scene_6": {
    "storyboard_description": "string",
    "image_prompt": "string", 
    "audio_narration": "string"
  }
}
Scene Creation Rules:

Create exactly {{7.`Number of Scenes`}} scenes numbered 1 through {{7.`Number of Scenes`}}
Scene 1 = Strong hook that grabs attention immediately
Middle scenes = Build tension and showcase key story elements
Final scene = Must include call-to-action (CTA) like "Available now" or "Get your copy today"
Each audio narration: 12-35 words, present tense, emotionally engaging
Target 3-4 seconds per scene for short-form video

Image Prompt Format:
"{{7.`Protagonist Names (from Book Details)`}} [Action/Pose] in [Setting], [Camera Angle], [Lighting Style], [Art Style], high quality, detailed, no text, no watermarks"
Style Guidelines:

Art Style: [ART_STYLE]{{7.`Artistic Style`}} (e.g., cinematic, illustrated, photorealistic)
Lighting: [LIGHTING] {{7.`Lighting and Mood`}}(e.g., dramatic shadows, soft natural light, moody)
Composition: [COMPOSITION]{{7.`Composition & Perspective`}} (e.g., close-up, wide shot, overhead view)

Book Context (Use for inspiration but don't copy):

Title: {{7.`Book Title (from Book Details)`}}
Author: {{7.`Pen Name (from Book Details)`}}
Genre: {{7.`Audience/Genre (from Book Details)`}}
Setting: {{7.`Setting (from Book Details)`}}
Main Characters: {{7.`Protagonist Names (from Book Details)`}}
Tone: {{7.`Tone/Mood (from Book Details)`}}
Plot Summary: {{7.`Blurb (from Book Details)`}}
Tropes: {{7.`Tropes (from Book Details)`}}

Marketing Objective: {{7.`Objective Name`}}
Target Platforms: {{7.Platform}}
Aspect Ratio: {{7.`Aspect Ratio`}}
